Spotlight Card Analysis

Star Players

Cards expected to be highly effective. This includes cards that demonstrate their true value in critical late-game situations.

  • Daiyousei, Lively Assistant
  • Energy Drink
  • Fairy's Wake Up
  • Frozen Specimen
  • Gift of Nature
  • Icicle Dance
  • Wolf Fur

Honor Students

Cards with exceptionally high tendency scores in both attack and defense or with silver(gold) medals, expected to perform consistently well in all situations.

  • Autumnal Harvest
  • Blizzard
  • Cool Entrance
  • Cool Party
  • Exteeending Aaaarm
  • First Aid Kit
  • Frozen Orb
  • Frozen Throne
  • Instant Freeze
  • Larva, God of Evernight
  • Moonlit Lotus
  • News Fabrication
  • On Thin Ice
  • Rainbow Danmaku Dupion
  • Refreshing Breeze
  • Stunning Summer Ice
  • The Reclusive Sage
  • Water Blanket

High-Potential Attackers

Cards with positive attack tendency and balanced defense.

  • Call on Friends
  • Ice Barrier
  • Sakura-Colored Sea
  • Wingbeats Flight

Solid Defenders

Cards with positive defense tendency and balanced attack.

  • Diamond Breath
  • Fairy On Ice
  • Ice Block
  • Princess Undine

Counter Cards

Cards with low overall stats that have proven to be decisive (medal-winning) in specific, high-impact situations.

  • Ice-Forged Blade

Card Classification Criteria

Each card is evaluated based on the following conditions in order from top to bottom, and is classified into the first type it matches.

Honor Students

  • Has a Gold Medal 🥇 or Silver Medal 🥈 (Highest Priority).
  • (Attack Tendency > 0.25 AND Defense Tendency > 0.25) AND has at least one Big Star ⭐ (tendency > 0.75).
  • Has a Bronze Medal 🥉 or better AND (Attack Tendency > 0.25 AND Defense Tendency > 0.25) AND has at least one Star ☆ (tendency > 0.5).
  • Otherwise, meets ( (Tendency Sum >= 0.75 AND has a medal) OR (Tendency Sum >= 1.0) ) AND (Overall Performance Score >= 100).

Star Players

  • Overall Performance Score < 100 BUT has a notable performance against the Act 4 Boss.
  • Has a medal AND all notable performances are concentrated in the late game (Act 3 or 4).
  • Attack Tendency > 1.0 OR Defense Tendency > 1.0.

High-Potential Attackers

  • Attack Tendency >= 0.25 AND Defense Tendency is within the range of -0.50 to +0.25.

Solid Defenders

  • Defense Tendency >= 0.25 AND Attack Tendency is within the range of -0.50 to +0.25.

Counter Cards

  • Tendency Sum < -1.5 AND has a medal.
